text: Tadger may refer to: * James Stewart (footballer, born 1883) (James "Tadger" Stewart, 1883-1952), English association footballer * Tommy Tadger, an alias for American pop rock musician Tommy James * St. Tadger's Day, a fictitious holiday in the BBC2 television comedy series Ripping Yarns * Tadger, a British slang term for the human penis ==See also== * Todger, see Human penis#Terminology * Penis (disambiguation)
title: Tadger
